snippet.title: The Secret Labyrinth
snippet.description:
My reskin of "The Secret Aquarium" inspired by Labyrinth Zone from Sonic 1, complete with a Sonic CD style arrangement/remix (by me), and the infamous air bubble system!

Dedicated OST upload for the track coming tomorrow!
